Lake Union Park

Overview

Description: Lake Union Park is about 12 acres named after the fresh water lake and shipping canal. Out there are some historic ships I would suggest stopping and taking a look at, the Lady Washington plays movies on the boat, you can climb aboard and watch for free. The MOHAI facility is also really neat to check out.
